Description of incident: The County of San Diego Human Resources Department notified employees of a data breach when information involving employees Wells Fargo Health Savings Accounts. The County stated,  "data regarding County employees who elected to set up HSAs was sent to Wells Fargo. The information compromised includes names, addresses, Social Security Number, birthdate, employee ID, primary email, work phone number, personal phone number.More information: http://oag.ca.gov/ecrime/databreach/reports/sb24-59801
